Lets try with AI and Enjoy coding with AI.
We should know Linux concepts and internals to modify AI generated code.
Teams co-pilot can write code in minutes which I take hours for mini assignment. But it has to be fine tuned or custumize to my needs.
AI could not write what design I thought of. For example it cannot use 2 dimensional array of pointers, but, which I could do.
Overall AI very great assistant for expereinced developers who know Linux intrnals, programming concepts. And Architects can design skeleton code.
